---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="positive-law"
    class="wheat-relative wheat-font-serif wheat-min-h-screen wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-py-12 wheat-py-24@md wheat-pos-law"
>
    <div class="wheat-container wheat-px-6">
        <div class="wheat-text-center wheat-mb-16">
            <span class="wheat-text-xs wheat-text-sm@md wheat-tracking-widest wheat-uppercase wheat-block wheat-mb-4 trigo-positive-chapter">
                La Ley
            </span>
            <h2 class="wheat-text-3xl wheat-text-5xl@md wheat-font-bold wheat-pos-law-title wheat-mb-6">El Orden del Caos</h2>
            <p class="wheat-text-lg wheat-pos-law-desc wheat-max-w-2xl wheat-mx-auto">
                <ShareableQuote
                    quote="La vida salvaje es libre, pero la justicia es arbitraria (la ley del más fuerte). El trigo nos obligó a inventar la Justicia Objetiva."
                />
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="wheat-pos-law-grid wheat-mb-12">
            <div class="wheat-relative wheat-pos-law-card-wrapper wheat-group">
                <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-inset-0 wheat-pos-law-card-glow wheat-rounded-lg"></div>
                <div class="wheat-relative wheat-pos-law-card wheat-p-8 wheat-rounded-lg wheat-border wheat-transition-all">
                    <div class="wheat-flex wheat-items-start wheat-gap-4 wheat-mb-4">
                        <div class="wheat-pos-law-card-icon-wrapper wheat-rounded-full">
                            <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                class="wheat-pos-law-card-icon"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M12 3v17.25m0 0c-1.472 0-2.882.265-4.185.75M12 20.25c1.472 0 2.882.265 4.185.75M18.75 4.97A48.416 48.416 0 0012 4.5c-2.291 0-4.545.16-6.75.47m13.5 0c1.01.143 2.01.317 3 .52m-3-.52l2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.988 5.988 0 01-2.031.352 5.988 5.988 0 01-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L18.75 4.971zm-16.5.52c.99-.203 1.99-.377 3-.52m0 0l2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.989 5.989 0 01-2.031.352 5.989 5.989 0 01-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L5.25 4.971z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="wheat-pos-law-card-title wheat-text-xl wheat-font-bold wheat-mb-2">
                                Resolución de Conflictos
                            </h3>
                            <div class="wheat-pos-law-card-divider wheat-mb-3"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="wheat-pos-law-card-text wheat-text-sm wheat-leading-relaxed">
                        Cuando dos vecinos discuten por un límite de tierra, ya no se matan. Van a
                        un tercero neutral. Nacen los jueces y las leyes escritas. La violencia
                        disminuye drásticamente dentro de los muros de la ciudad.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="wheat-relative wheat-pos-law-card-wrapper wheat-group">
                <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-inset-0 wheat-pos-law-card-glow wheat-rounded-lg"></div>
                <div class="wheat-relative wheat-pos-law-card wheat-p-8 wheat-rounded-lg wheat-border wheat-transition-all">
                    <div class="wheat-flex wheat-items-start wheat-gap-4 wheat-mb-4">
                        <div class="wheat-pos-law-card-icon-wrapper wheat-rounded-full">
                            <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                class="wheat-pos-law-card-icon"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="wheat-pos-law-card-title wheat-text-xl wheat-font-bold wheat-mb-2">
                                Derechos de Propiedad
                            </h3>
                            <div class="wheat-pos-law-card-divider wheat-mb-3"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="wheat-pos-law-card-text wheat-text-sm wheat-leading-relaxed">
                        Saber que lo que siembras es tuyo permitió la inversión a largo plazo. Nadie
                        construye una casa de piedra si cree que se la quitarán mañana. La ley trajo
                        la estabilidad necesaria para el progreso.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="wheat-relative wheat-max-w-3xl wheat-mx-auto">
            <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-inset-0 wheat-pos-law-bottom-glow"></div>
            <div class="wheat-relative wheat-pos-law-bottom-card wheat-border wheat-rounded-lg wheat-p-8 wheat-text-center">
                <div class="wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-gap-8 wheat-mb-4">
                    <div class="wheat-text-center">
                        <div class="wheat-pos-law-val--before wheat-text-4xl wheat-font-bold wheat-mb-1">∞</div>
                        <div class="wheat-text-xs wheat-pos-law-bottom-label wheat-uppercase wheat-tracking-wider">Antes</div>
                    </div>
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="wheat-pos-law-arrow"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <div class="wheat-text-center">
                        <div class="wheat-pos-law-val--after wheat-text-4xl wheat-font-bold wheat-mb-1">-90%</div>
                        <div class="wheat-text-xs wheat-pos-law-bottom-label wheat-uppercase wheat-tracking-wider">Después</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="wheat-pos-law-bottom-label wheat-text-xs wheat-uppercase wheat-tracking-widest">
                    Reducción de Violencia Interpersonal
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .wheat-pos-law {
        color: #e7e5e4;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-desc {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-card-glow {
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1), transparent);
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-card-wrapper:hover .wheat-pos-law-card-glow {
        opacity: 1;
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-card {
        background-color: #1c1917;
        border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
        height: 100%;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-card-wrapper:hover .wheat-pos-law-card {
        border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-card-icon-wrapper {
        width: 3rem;
        height: 3rem;
        background-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-card-icon {
        width: 1.5rem;
        height: 1.5rem;
        color: #10b981;
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-card-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-card-divider {
        width: 3rem;
        height: 4px;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.5), transparent);
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-card-text {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-bottom-glow {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05), rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1), rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05));
        filter: blur(24px);
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-bottom-card {
        background-color: #0c0a09;
        border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-val--before {
        color: #ef4444;
        opacity: 0.8;
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-val--after {
        color: #10b981;
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-arrow {
        width: 2rem;
        height: 2rem;
        color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.5);
    }
    .wheat-pos-law-bottom-label {
        color: #78716c;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wheat-pos-law-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }
    }
</style>
